# SolVerdict — LLM provider keys ONLY.
#
# There are intentionally NO fields for Solana private keys, seeds, mnemonics
# or wallet paths. All test wallets are ephemeral keypairs generated in-memory
# at runtime (Keypair.generate()) and funded on a local fork via cheatcodes.
# If you find yourself wanting to add a wallet key here: don't. See SECURITY.md.

ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
